  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (Interior Design)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Have years of experience in similar role (Interior, construction, civil)<br>\nLiaise with consultants and construction team, including Project Director/Managers, Engineers etc. for cost related issues<br>\nPrepare Bill of Quantities (BOQ) in accordance to specifications and drawings for calling of quotation<br>\nSourcing of sub-contractors for related scope of works<br>\nCarry out cost comparison and shortlisting sub-contractors for the award of sub-contracts, including negotiation of quotation before finalizing the cost comparison &amp; recommendation<br>\nPrepare and issue sub-contract documents/works order for approved sub-contracts' works<br>\nMonthly progress claim assessment and payment of sub-contractors in fair manner, and to ensure works carried out in compliance to contracts and specifications.<br>\nPrepare and claim variations to consultant<br>\nSite visits to understand the progress of construction and works involved<br>\nWorking as a team member with colleagues to support each other on past to current work experienc</p>",
